<tmpl:TITLE_WIN>Capture attempt averted at cave {cave} ({xpos}/{ypos})
</tmpl:TITLE_WIN><tmpl:TITLE_LOSE>Capture attempt succeeded at cave {cave} ({xpos}/{ypos}) successful
</tmpl:TITLE_LOSE>

<tmpl:MSG>
<p>
{if att_won}
With bloodshot eyes you are watching a hostile tribe from
{else}
Profoundly amused, you are watching a hostile tribe from
{/if}
{if self}your cave {orig}{else}
the cave {orig} {if sender}of player {sender}{/if}
{/if}
{if att_won}
trying to capture your cave {cave}! You have lost the battle for your cave!
{else}
fleeing from the superior troops defending your cave {cave}, after they had
attempted to capture your cave! You have won the battle for your cave!
{/if}
</p>
{if att_won}
<p>
{if takeover}
You have lost the command over this cave to {sender}.
{else}
Despite this defeat the cave is still under your control!
{/if}
</p>
{/if}

