<tmpl:RESOURCES>
{if att_won}
<p>
The hostile tribe has plundered your cave. You were able to hide some of
your resources, but nonetheless it captured:
</p>
{else}
<p>
While fleeing from your troops, the hostile tribe loses the following resources:
</p>
